<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-07-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-07-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="596" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d596">
                        <head><hi rend="italic"><persName type="from">Cardinal Rampolla</persName>
                                to Mr. <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-07-23"><hi rend="italic">July 23,
                                1903</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I have not failed to convey to the Sacred College the heartfelt sympathy
                            expressed by you in the President’s name on the sad occasion of His
                            Holiness’s death.</p>
                        <p>The Sacred College desires me to express to the President its deep and
                            sincere gratitude for such a noble manifestation.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Rampolla.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>